name: Meet Sylvie!
description:
Meet Sylvie!

Sylvie is a brand new waldorf style doll. Made from all natural materials. Her skin is made from soft high quality cotton knit fabric imported from the Netherlands and she is stuffed with clean sweet smelling unspun wool.
She is about 15" tall.


Her hair is made made from a wonderful soft handspun wool yarn, and can be styled in many ways.


Sylvie comes wearing a beautiful Euro style outfit with a long sleeve shirt made with imported Stenzo fabric, pair of matching real pocket  pants in pink corduroy, a pair of hand knit wool shoes, and little cotton panties.

Sylvie is ready to find a new loving family to take care of her.



Shipping includes insurance.
